    "Strengthen the exploration of new technologies to replace the use of impact fruit harvesting methods to ensure fruit quality.",
    "The comb fruit harvester uses a combing device to act on the canopy of the fruit tree, increasing the rotation and oscillation of the combing device to dislodge the fruit (Castro-García et al. 2012).",
    "This equipment can be used for fruits such as goji berries and blueberries.",
    "In terms of blueberry harvesting, the current state-of-the-art technology is best typified by vibratory mechanical harvesting technology.",
    "According to the growth characteristics of blueberry fruits, a combing device is used to act directly on the canopy of the blueberry plant, and the fruits are dislodged through the combing device."
